  "title": "Technical Engineer (Civil / Structural / Design) - Training Provided!",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Engineering Consulting industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Civil/ Structural Engineer </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position: </strong>Civil/ Structural Engineer</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, Office Hours</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $4,200 + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Create detailed 2D/3D models and engineering drawings.</li>\n  <li>Prepare engineering documentation.</li>\n  <li>Conduct feasibility assessments and technical evaluations.</li>\n  <li>Perform research aligned with organizational objectives.</li>\n  <li>Manage project timelines and coordinate execution.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with current industry standards and regulations.</li>\n  <li>Perform on-site inspections as needed.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with multiple parties to address design and implementation challenges.</li>\n  <li>Participate in professional development programs prepared by the company.</li>\n  <li>Conduct technical research and support collaborative R&amp;D initiatives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least a Bachelor of Civil Engineering, Architecture, or other related discipline with minimum 1 year of similar working experience.</li>\n  <li>Inexperienced candidates are welcome to apply as training will be provided.</li>\n  <li>Experience in project management would be advantageous.</li>\n  <li>Willing to travel as and when needed.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office.</li>\n  <li>Familiar with CAD and other engineering design software.</li>\n  <li>Having a Class 3 Driving License would be a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
